  "description": "Deterministic forge and evidence gate for the canonical standalone replacement artifact. This gate materializes libfrankenlibc_replace.so from the current frankenlibc-abi release cdylib, records loader/symbol/dependency evidence, and keeps replacement claims blocked when evidence is absent, stale, misnamed, non-ELF, or still host-glibc-dependent.",
